    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4_3",
    "text": "（四）组建团队及搭建伙伴关系",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.07394489012905477,
      0.6080368906455863,
      0.19997674688989653,
      0.6245059288537549
    ],
    "page": "yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4_4",
    "text": "企业如果想打造AI能，少需要以下类才所组成的团队。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07394489012905477,
      0.6277997364953887,
      0.3315893500755726,
      0.6442687747035574
    ],
    "page": "yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4_5",
    "text": "（1）AI技术专家包括数学、统计学的科学家，进底层算法的研究；同时 也包括传统意义上的IT技术专家，能使用最新的AI算法开发技术原型以及后续的商业 产品。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.053017091035926056,
      0.647562582345191,
      0.4129752354377398,
      0.7035573122529645
    ],
    "page": "yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4_6",
    "text": "（2）业专家对于特定业的AI解决案，团队中需要有经验的业专家。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07347982792698524,
      0.7068511198945981,
      0.39995349377979306,
      0.7239789196310935
    ],
    "page": "yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4_7",
    "text": "（3）AI应用专家—AI应用专家先是一名优秀的产品经理，其次要了解算法特性， 最后还要能理解业问题，这样才能将AI技术专家和业专家的优势整合在一起构建适 合业的技术解决方案。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.05348215323799558,
      0.7272727272727273,
      0.4125101732356703,
      0.7832674571805006
    ],
    "page": "yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4_8",
    "text": "组建内部智能团队的同时，企业也可通过伙伴关系快速引进智能相关专业 知识，特别是在智能战略、实施流程、技术实践、项交付等可以借助合作伙 伴的协助填补能空白。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.05348215323799558,
      0.7865612648221344,
      0.4129752354377398,
      0.8432147562582345
    ],
    "page": "yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4_9",
    "text": "（五）验证及大规模实施",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.07440995233112428,
      0.8504611330698287,
      0.17253807696779444,
      0.8669301712779973
    ],
    "page": "yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_d3c82bef4d6b8f3a9d1c1b3e7a02d8ba86c91e585d83766d70b6f540456a6a54.pdf_4_10",
    "text": "有了应用场景，完善了数据基础，搭建好团队以后，接下去要做的是基于AI的过程 设计原型验证(proofofconcept)。在确认技术原型可的情况下进迭代和最终的规模 实施。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.05348215323799558,
